entries.journal_entry_description: Infiltrate the Imperial Mine and extract samples of DNA from the Enraged Miners. Use the DNA extractor provided when you encounter an enraged miner.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Use the DNA Extractor to retrieve samples of DNA from the Enraged Miners.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Return to Rek Thelcar with the extracted DNA samples
